    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both mechanical reliability and aesthetic poise. This unit has undergone a rigorous professional assessment to ensure that its powertrain and interior appointments meet our exacting standards for roadworthiness and comfort. Featuring a refined profile and a responsive driving dynamic, this vehicle represents a superior acquisition for the discerning operator who values performance without compromise. We invite you to evaluate the integrity of this exceptional offering in person.",
      "price": 32800.0,
