      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute favorite ride, and it's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my trips around town. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it the perfect catch for someone who wants a reliable set of wheels without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m so excited for the next person to get as much happiness out of it as I have\u2014come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The high-revving powerplant is paired with a longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power delivery to the rear wheels. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive double VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis has been strategically reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to improve torsional rigidity and mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Suspension components feature refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the hallmark communicative steering and neutral handling balance this platform is known for. A mechanically robust example optimized for spirited driving and peak lateral acceleration.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Reliable engine. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear. Maintenance up to date. Title in hand.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, well-cared-for car that looks as good as it drives. The exterior finish retains a high-gloss luster, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia that testify to its honest road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and odor-free; the bolsters on the seats are firm, and the dashboard remains free of any cracks or sun damage. All electronic components\u2014including the premium sound system, dual-zone climate control, and navigation\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is quiet and responsive, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule and recent fluid changes. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, turn-key vehicle that bridges the gap between a daily driver and a pride-of-ownership showpiece.",
      "price": 33850.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and an interior preserved with exceptional care, it offers a refined driving experience that exceeds standard expectations for its class. Every component has been thoroughly inspected to ensure long-term reliability and peak performance. We invite you to experience the superior craftsmanship and proven durability of this distinguished automobile.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth ride without any fuss! It looks great and drives even better. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 featuring eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematics with aluminum multi-link suspension and EDC (Electronic Damper Control). Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the mechanical integrity remains high, with a linear power band and a rigid subframe. A true driver\u2019s example with a clean oil analysis history.",
